Company Profile
LUBUS is a full-service digital company based in Mumbai, India that
focuses on driving results via effective and measurable solutions.
A patron once said we’re the best of both worlds. An experimental
powerhouse with boutique service. That’s because we stay small and

And always putting their experience into practice on every project.
And yes, empathy and objectivity are our key personality traits but we
do have a wild side – it usually emerges when we’re arguing about
when and where to have tea.
Till date, we are proud to have worked with clients from India , United

Our Approach
We take a structured approach to every project. Our work process was created
to ensure every project is delivered on time and on budget. Once your project
kicks off, here’s what to expect.
We Start With Why?
(We love Simon Sinek!) This helps us fully understand your goals or problems
and sometimes maybe even leading to redefine your situation altogether. 
No Surprises 
 Our solutions are born from honest, collaborative client-agency partnerships —
not presenting solutions we’ve cooked up on our own. So be ready for open
discussions! 
Gather Inspiration 
 This is mainly a research phase wherein we try to look at similar cases,
viewpoints and competitors to understand what worked for them and use those
findings. 
Zero Down
